document_data.name: Skella Ironeye
document_data.mainbody: '''Skella Ironeye''' was a [[dwarf]] (half-[[duergar]], half [[shield dwarf]]) prospector member of [[Clan Ironeye]] in [[Undermountain]] in the early 1490s [[DR]].
document_data.Activities: Skella led the duergar offensive inside the [[Lost Level]].
document_data.History:
In [[1492 DR]],{{Waterdeep-time}} during their march Skella stole the ''[[dagger of blindsight]]'' from [[Azrok]].

She was directing the conquest of the local temple of [[Dumathoin]], which was protected by a [[clay golem]].
document_data.Personality: Skella was more lawful than the average duergar but would turn against those she suspected of treachery. She was obsessed by artistry and beauty.
